n### 响应式设计\\n- 适配桌面和移动端屏幕\\n- 棋盘大小根据视口自适应\\n\\n### 部署方式\\n- 单个 index.html 文件（CSS/JS 内联或同目录引用）\\n- 浏览器直接打开即可运行\\n\\n## 非功能性要求\\n- 零安装依赖\\n- 加载时间 < 1 秒\\n- 流畅的交互体验（60fps 动画）\\n\\n## 不包含\\n- 在线多人对战（无后端）\\n- 用户账号系统\\n- 排行榜\\n- 音效\\n\"},\"output\":\"{\\n  \\\"success\\\": true,\\n  \\\"path\\\": \\\".specforge/specs/WI-016/intake.md\\\",\\n  \\\"size\\\": 1733\\n}\",\"metadata\":{\"truncated\":false},\"title\":\"\",\"time\":{\"start\":1780039032424,\"end\":1780039032436}},\"id\":\"prt_e72981e60001aJ002B6NU3uEUz\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_18d704b29ffeVIJ9w8hL0JITOi\",\"messageID\":\"msg_e7297ca220019iDuBM5GoNBzlc\"},{\"reason\":\"tool-calls\",\"type\":\"step-finish\",\"tokens\":{\"total\":26492,\"input\":5136,\"output\":563,\"reasoning\":121,\"cache\":{\"write\":0,\"read\":20672}},\"cost\":0,\"id\":\"prt_e72981e7d001qP71Z20QSuTlOV\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_18d704b29ffeVIJ9w8hL0JITOi\",\"messageID\":\"msg_e7297ca220019iDuBM5GoNBzlc\"}]},{\"info\":{\"parentID\":\"msg_e7297c9f1001psXsMUG6a05mYB\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"mode\":\"sf-orchestrator\",\"agent\":\"sf-orchestrator\",\"path\":{\"cwd\":\"D:\\\\code\\\\temp\\\\wzq\",\"root\":\"/\"},\"cost\":0,\"tokens\":{\"total\":26652,\"input\":11361,\"output\":123,\"reasoning\":0,\"cache\":{\"write\":0,\"read\":15168}},\"modelID\":\"glm-5.1\",\"providerID\":\"zhipu-coding-plan\",\"time\":{\"created\":1780039032456,\"completed\":1780039041554},\"finish\":\"tool-calls\",\"id\":\"msg_e72981e88001ph3xfdIuPlK4nK\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_18d704b29ffeVIJ9w8hL0JITOi\"},\"parts\":[{\"type\":\"step-start\",\"id\":\"prt_e729835e6001KlFbyswLzduGpY\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_18d704b29ffeVIJ9w8hL0JITOi\",\"messageID\":\"msg_e72981e88001ph3xfdIuPlK4nK\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Intake 完成！默认方案总结：\\n\\n> **网页版五子棋** — 15×15 棋盘 | 人人+人机对战 | 经典木纹风格 | Canvas 绘制 | 纯 HTML/CSS/JS | 悔棋+重开+AI对手\\n\\n现在流转到 **requirements** 阶段，调度需求分析 Agent：\",\"time\":{\"start\":1780039038440,\"end\":1780039041536},\"id\":\"prt_e729835e8001ihSScgUVBG4TCq\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_18d704b29f